{
  "texts": [
    "Also, this personalized device, capable of real-time collection of reliable and accurate multi-modal data regardless of external environmental factors, should be accompanied by the corresponding classification technique to encode the gathered data into personalized feedback parameters for target applications.",
    "Here, we proposed a human emotion recognition system in an attempt to utilize complex emotional states with our personalized skin-integrated facial interface (PSiFI) offering simultaneous detection and integration of facial expression and vocal speech.",
    "The PSiFI incorporates a personalized facial mask that is self-powered, easily applicable, stretchable, transparent, capable of wireless communication, and highly customized to conformally fit into an individual's face curvatures based on 3D face reconstruction.",
    "These features enhance the device's usability and reliability in capturing and analyzing emotional cues, facilitating the real-time detection of multi-modal sensing signals derived from facial strains and vocal vibrations.",
    "To encode the combinatorial sensing signals into personalized feedback parameters, we employ a convolutional neural network (CNN)-based classification technique that rapidly adapts to an individual's context through transfer learning."
  ]
}